GMT 18 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1802170594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Moscow, 18 Feb -- "In the last few days Russian 
Federation President Boris Yeltsin has been exchanging messages 
with leaders of the states most actively participating in the 
