Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From "News Bulletin" No. 36/94] </F>
  [Text] Tuesday, February 22 -- The Baltic defence forces 
chiefs of staff agreed on the structure and complement of the 
Baltic joint peacekeeping battalion. The unit is to consist of 
710-715 men. Each of the Baltic States will form one company of 
160 men, including 9 officers and 28 non-commissioned officers. 

