<F P=103> WS2202210594 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ukrainian Foreign Minister Anatoliy Zlenko is 
continuing his visit to Germany. In an interview to the leading 
German newspaper FRANKFURTER ALLGEMEINE ZEITUNG, Anatoliy Zlenko 
said: We did not make a mistake when we thought that the 
