<F P=103> LD2102120194 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Anatoliy Zlenko, Ukraine's minister of foreign 
affairs, arrived in Bratislava on an official visit today. A 
special correspondent reports that in the course of the day the 
head of our state's foreign policy will hold talks with 
Slovakia's leaders. He is to meet Michal Kovac, president of 
