  [Text] Azerbaijani Prime Minister Suret Guseynov received 
today the Georgian Prime Minister Otar Patsatsia and his deputy 
Zorab Kervalishvili. 
  [Begin Sadiq Guzelov recording] Matters of mutual interest 
were discussed at the meeting. Otar Patsatsia requested a 
supply of fuel to Georgia. He also asked for support in 
organizing the visit of Georgian and Azerbaijani experts to Iran 
